ira/rest/api/2/user?username=prasanth_j","name":"prasanth_j","key":"prasanth_j","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Prasanth Jayachandran","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2015-01-21T22:28:29.656+0000","updated":"2015-01-21T22:28:29.656+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12765575/comment/14287088","id":"14287088","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gopalv","name":"gopalv","key":"gopalv","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Gopal V","active":true,"timeZone":"Asia/Kolkata"},"body":"Do you know if the history dir exists? The condition for history seems to be - if ((new File(historyDirectory)).exists()) {","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gopalv","name":"gopalv","key":"gopalv","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Gopal V","active":true,"timeZone":"Asia/Kolkata"},"created":"2015-01-22T08:02:10.089+0000","updated":"2015-01-22T08:02:10.089+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12765575/comment/14288028","id":"14288028","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=prasanth_j","name":"prasanth_j","key":"prasanth_j","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Prasanth Jayachandran","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"[~gopalv] Yes. The history dir is the user's home directory which exists. The history file .hivehistory also exists (will be created if it doesn't exist). But still the commands are not logged to the hive history file.\n\nTo reproduce\n1) Remove the .hivehistory file\n2) Restart hive cli\n3) Run some commands and quit cli\n4) When we rerun the hive cli again, press up arrow nothing will show up from history. \n\nI suspect, the flushing doesn't happen because of quit command which issues System.exit(0) and quits the cli without ever calling the history.flush(). Same happens with SIGINT as well. I think we need to flush the history before processing every command. Adding the history flushing just before executing the command seems to fix the issue. I can put up a patch for it if you can confirm that the current way of flushing does not work.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=prasanth_j","name":"prasanth_j","key":"prasanth_j","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Prasanth Jayachandran","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2015-01-22T19:16:19.681+0000","updated":"2015-01-22T19:16:19.681+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12765575/comment/14288043","id":"14288043","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=prasanth_j","name":"prasanth_j","key":"prasanth_j","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Prasanth Jayachandran","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Or we have to flush the history before closing the session (finally block after execute cli driver).","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=prasanth_j","name":"prasanth_j","key":"prasanth_j","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Prasanth Jayachandran","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2015-01-22T19:21:55.562+0000","updated":"2015-01-22T19:21:55.562+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12765575/comment/14288090","id":"14288090","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gopalv","name":"gopalv","key":"gopalv","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&av